{"Id":480,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":103,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"以时光盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":103,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"一切人确是在亏折之中，"},{"SurahNumber":103,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"惟信道而且行善，并以真理相劝，以坚忍相勉的人则不然。"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"伤哉！每个诽谤者, 诋毁者"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"他聚积财产, 而当作武器"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"他以为他的财产, 能使他不灭。"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"绝不然, 他必定要被投在毁灭坑中。"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"你怎能知道毁灭坑是什麽？"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"是真主的燃著的烈活。"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"能升到人的心上。"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"他们必定要被关在烈火中"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"吊在许多很高的柱子上。"},{"SurahNumber":105,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"难道你不知道你的主怎样处治象的主人们吗？"},{"SurahNumber":105,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"难道他没有使他们的计谋, 变成无益的吗？"},{"SurahNumber":105,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"他曾派遣成群的鸟去伤他们"},{"SurahNumber":105,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"以粘土石射击他们"},{"SurahNumber":105,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"使他们变成吃剩的干草一样。"}]}